    Contexed, ResultMapper<java.util.Map<K,java.lang.Number>>

    public class MinimumMapMapper<K>
extends MapMapper<K,java.lang.Number>
    A MapMapper where the data field is Numerical that the minimum is selected from. As the key is a SQLValue rather than a SQLExpression we may have multiple SQL rows mapping to the same key so numerical results may have to be combined.
